snippet: At the site of a nondescript warehouse, The Albanese Organization is planning a $140 million, nine-story office building on property abutting the High Line.
abstract: Albanese Organization closes deal for a nondescript warehouse in West Chelsea that it plans to use for a $140 million, nine-story office building project next to the popular High Line elevated park; says the time is right for the neighborhood which has received a boost in popularity in recent years due to development.
lead_paragraph: At the site of a nondescript warehouse, The Albanese Organization is planning a $140 million, nine-story office building on property abutting the High Line.

headline.seo: Albanese Plans Office Building for Stylish West Chelsea
headline.main: Developers Sense the Time Is Right to Play Off the Aura of West Chelsea
headline.print_headline: Developers Sense the Time Is Right To Play Off the Aura of West Chelsea
